    <note>Yang(2) Guobao [7098] Huaibao's [2006] elder brother. Son of Lu(9) Gongzhu's [1314] sister. Shao(2) Yong's [3718] menren. Fujian TZ, 147.23b lists a Guobao as a Jianning, Jianan county jinshi in 1067, which makes chronoloigcal sense. My guess is that these are related to the Jianning Yang and that his unnamed father, L [22537], moved to Zhengzhou. XCB, 408.9a, 410.7a, 413.11a-14b. CBD, 4, 3182.From Hartwell's ACTIVITY table:1088:  Apt. provisional CHengdu yunpan1088:  Out of office as provisional CHengdu yunpan1088:  Apt. and out after two days as Shanxi yunpan</note>
